*<div id="function.shmop-close" class="refentry">  <div class="refnamediv">   <h1 class="refname">shmop_close</h1>   <p class="verinfo">(PHP 4 &gt;= 4.0.4, PHP 5, PHP 7)</p><p class="refpurpose"><span class="refname">shmop_close</span> &mdash; <span class="dc-title">Close shared memory block</span></p>   </div>  <div class="refsect1 description" id="refsect1-function.shmop-close-description">   <h3 class="title">说明</h3>   <div class="methodsynopsis dc-description">    <span class="type"><span class="type void">void</span></span> <span class="methodname"><strong>shmop_close</strong></span>     ( <span class="methodparam"><span class="type">resource</span> <code class="parameter">$shmid</code></span>    )</div>    <p class="para rdfs-comment">    <span class="function"><strong>shmop_close()</strong></span> is used to close a shared memory block.   </p>  </div>   <div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-function.shmop-close-parameters">   <h3 class="title">参数</h3>   <p class="para">    <dl>            <dt> <code class="parameter">shmid</code></dt>       <dd>        <p class="para">        The shared memory block resource created by         <span class="function">{@link shmop_open()}</span>       </p>      </dd>          </dl>    </p>  </div>   <div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.shmop-close-returnvalues">   <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>   <p class="para">    没有返回值。   </p>  </div>    <div class="refsect1 changelog" id="refsect1-function.shmop-close-changelog">   <h3 class="title">更新日志</h3>   <table class="doctable informaltable">         <thead>      <tr>       <th>版本</th>       <th>说明</th>      </tr>      </thead>      <tbody class="tbody">      <tr>       <td>7.0.0</td>       <td>        The type of <code class="parameter">shmid</code> has been changed from        <span class="type"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.integer.php" class="type int">int</a></span> to <span class="type"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.resource.php" class="type resource">resource</a></span>.       </td>      </tr>      </tbody>       </table>   </div>    <div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.shmop-close-examples">   <h3 class="title">范例</h3>   <p class="para">    <div class="example" id="example-4451">     <p><strong>Example #1 Closing shared memory block</strong></p>     <div class="example-contents"> <div class="phpcode"><code><span style="color: #000000"> <span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br />shmop_close</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$shm_id</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span> </span> </code></div>     </div>     </div>   </p>   <p class="para">    This example will close shared memory block identified by <em>$shm_id</em>.   </p>  </div>   <div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.shmop-close-seealso">   <h3 class="title">参见</h3>   <p class="para">    <ul class="simplelist">     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link shmop_open()} - Create or open shared memory block</span></li>    </ul>   </p>  </div>  <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/ref.shmop.php">Shared Memory 函数</a></div></div>
